 of the liquid core. https://imagizer.imageshack.com/v2/640x480q90/838/wnetrzeziemi.jpg This unequal pressure distribution causes deformations of Earths crust and mantle. We can see those deformations on
 all of the images of geopotential model (GRIM, EGM96 and others)'https://scx2.b-cdn.net/gfx/news/hires/2009/earthexplore.jpg Together with the movement of the solid inner core inside the mantle also the
 zones of increased and decreased pressure inside Earth move and together with them the deformations of Earth's crust drift west. That west drift of the Earth's crust deformations is a driving mechanism
